data.description: Welcome to your dream townhome! This beautiful property boasts elegance, convenience, and comfort all in one. Nestled in a prime location this townhome offers easy access to all the amenities Alpharetta has to offer, including top-rated schools, shopping, dining, and entertainment. With its desirable location and stylish features, this townhome presents an incredible opportunity to live the ultimate Alpharetta lifestyle. Don't miss out - schedule your showing today!
